  "body": "A call to a contract results in running node to stop.\r\nhardhat v2.11.2:\r\n\r\nLast message from node:\r\n```\r\neth_call\r\n\r\n  If you think this is a bug in Hardhat, please report it here: https://hardhat.org/report-bug\r\n\r\nMined empty block #15682283 with base fee 47143756\r\nY:\\Blockchain\\weeb-finance-solidity\\node_modules\\hardhat\\internal\\hardhat-network\\stack-traces\\solidity-errors.js:111\r\n    return new SolidityCallSite(sourceReference.sourceName, sourceReference.contract, sourceReference.function !== undefined\r\n                                                ^\r\n\r\nTypeError: Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'sourceName')\r\n(Use `node --trace-uncaught ...` to show where the exception was thrown)\r\n```\r\n\r\nScript error:\r\n```\r\nError: missing revert data in call exception; Transaction reverted without a reason string [ See: https://links.ethers.org/v5-errors-CALL_EXCEPTION ] (data=\"0x\", transaction={\"from\":\"0xf39Fd6e\r\n51aad88F6F4ce6aB8827279cffFb92266\",\"to\":\"0x00CAC06Dd0BB4103f8b62D280fE9BCEE8f26fD59\",\"data\":\"0x759eee10000000000000000000000000f95fa88bb0d0937100982061f4bb2cea7caf37eb0000000000000000000000006\r\n87d9755aef27f19cf70b7df9c40d76464852271\",\"accessList\":null}, error={\"errno\":-4077,\"code\":\"ECONNRESET\",\"syscall\":\"read\"}, code=CALL_EXCEPTION, version=providers/5.7.1)\r\n    at Logger.makeError (C:\\my-solidity\\node_modules\\@ethersproject\\logger\\src.ts\\index.ts:269:28)\r\n    at Logger.throwError (C:\\my-solidity\\node_modules\\@ethersproject\\logger\\src.ts\\index.ts:281:20)\r\n    at checkError (C:\\my-solidity\\node_modules\\@ethersproject\\providers\\src.ts\\json-rpc-provider.ts:66:16)\r\n    at EthersProviderWrapper.<anonymous> (C:\\my-solidity\\node_modules\\@ethersproject\\providers\\src.ts\\json-rpc-provider.ts:642:20)\r\n    at step (C:\\my-solidity\\node_modules\\@ethersproject\\providers\\lib\\json-rpc-provider.js:48:23)\r\n    at Object.throw (C:\\my-solidity\\node_modules\\@ethersproject\\providers\\lib\\json-rpc-provider.js:29:53)\r\n    at rejected (C:\\my-solidity\\node_modules\\@ethersproject\\providers\\lib\\json-rpc-provider.js:21:65) {\r\n  reason: 'missing revert data in call exception; Transaction reverted without a reason string',\r\n  code: 'CALL_EXCEPTION',\r\n  data: '0x',\r\n  transaction: {\r\n    from: '0xf39Fd6e51aad88F6F4ce6aB8827279cffFb92266',\r\n    to: '0x00CAC06Dd0BB4103f8b62D280fE9BCEE8f26fD59',\r\n    data: '0x759eee10000000000000000000000000f95fa88bb0d0937100982061f4bb2cea7caf37eb000000000000000000000000687d9755aef27f19cf70b7df9c40d76464852271',\r\n    accessList: null\r\n  },\r\n  error: Error: read ECONNRESET\r\n      at TCP.onStreamRead (node:internal/stream_base_commons:217:20) {\r\n    errno: -4077,\r\n    code: 'ECONNRESET',\r\n    syscall: 'read'\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n```",
